Geodata base is the hand drawn Schmettau Map (1:50.000, ca. 1780) and the Prussian Land Survey (scale 1:25.000, ca. 1890). Additional information from other sources where aligned and added. In total about 200 maps and the same number of archival documents where checked for reconstruction of spatial explicit tree species localities.
